        <div class="panel-body">
            <div class="qsn1">
                <form id="myform" name="myform" method="post" action="/q_variable">
                    <h4>Just to make sure that we are on the same page. Could you please explain what a variable is?</h4><hr/>
                    <h4>A variable is : <span ng-bind = "v_answer" style="color: #6F5499 "></span></h4>
                    <input type="text" name="variable" ng-model="v_answer" style="border-color: #6F5499" class="form-control input"><br><br>
                    <button class="btn btn-outlined btn-theme btn-md"  data-wow-delay="0.7s" style="border-radius: 0px">Answer</button><br>
